node.text:
Doing this was life changing. 

Keep your focus on the things that you can control. 

Don’t give anything else your energy. 

Everything else is just outside noise.

TAX TIP: If you own a business/self employed, and have an office you use specifically for business, you can still claim the “home office deduction” even if you’re renting. 

Hope this tip helps a few people out who did not know this! 🔥

Want to learn more about the tax code? Give the tax expert @doughertytaxsolutions a follow!
Happy Friday! Just a reminder to buy some assets if you got paid today. I just bought some more $VOO and $QQQ today. What did you buy?

Nothing else comes even close!

Buy assets, and let those assets pay for the lifestyle you want later. 💯🔥
Stay grateful and keep pushing forward! 💯🔥
